To Create S3 Bucket
Path: Amazon S3 ==> Buckets ==> s3-demo-ynd (Bucket Name)

To Upload Objects:
Amazon S3 ==> Buckets ==> s3-demo-ynd ==> Upload

Bucket Versioning:
Amazon S3 ==> Buckets ==> s3-demo-ynd ==> Properties ==>Bucket Versioning should be enbaled 
When Obects are uploading into bucket, versions will be maintained 

To Access Objects in Internet:
Amazon S3 ==> Buckets ==> s3-demo-ynd ==> Permissions ==> Block public access ==> uncheck Block all public access ==> Save Changes

Amazon S3 ==> Buckets ==> s3-demo-ynd ==> Permissions ==> Bucket policy

{
    "Version": "2012-10-17",
    "Statement": [
        {
            "Sid": "Statement1",
            "Effect": "Allow",
            "Principal": "*",
            "Action": "s3:GetObject",
            "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::s3-demo-ynd/*"
        }
    ]
}

